You are here: Salesfroce Help > Docs > Product Service Campaign

Organize focused product service campaigns to service faulty products, recall defective assets, and manage customer communications at scale. Manage Mass Asset Recalls, Services, and Upgrades Efficiently.

Identify and Segment Assets in Product Service Campaigns Easily.
Swiftly curate lists of assets that you want to recall, audit, fix, or upgrade by creating actionable lists for product service campaigns.
Manage work orders and return orders to capture the services to be performed on impacted products.
Specify sophisticated filter conditions or use Data Cloud segments to group assets that you want to include in actionable lists.
